        text: "'*******************************************************************************"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'Redirects the instance of a class to another instance of the same class within"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'   the scope of a private class Function (not  Sub) where the call happens."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'Warning! ONLY call this method from a Private Function of a class!"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'vbArray + vbString Function return type is not supported. It would be"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'   possible to find the correct address by reading memory in a loop but there"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'   would be no checking available"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
